.DT
set_hide_cond
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_hide_cond

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_hide_cond -  This sets whether the condition string should be returned or not.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_hide_cond(int i)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^i%^RESET%^ - set it to 1 to hide the condition string.

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/condition.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This sets whether the condition string should be returned or not.  This
is for objects what indicate their condition with different long
descriptions instead of the default condition string.
.EP

